ModelHeader.Author: Yu-ichi Ozaki
ModelHeader.ModelTitle: ERK signaling network in PC12 cells

note.value: Sasagawa, S., Ozaki, Y. Fujita, K. and Kuroda, S. (2005) Prediction and validation of the distinct dynamics of transient and sustained ERK activation. Nature Cell Biology, 7 (4), 365-373

This is a replication of our ERK model that presented in the above reference publication. The model was constructed using JDesigner version 1.963. In this model, enzyme-substrate complexes were treated as separate species in some enzymatic reactions, due to the difference in handling these complexes between GENESIS/Kinetikit and JDesigner.
